snippet: A 42-year-old woman and her 8-year-old daughter were killed at the intersection of 210th Street and 64th Avenue, in the Oakland Gardens section of the borough.
abstract: Two people are killed and four others are seriously injured in car crash in Queens; cause of crash is not yet known.
lead_paragraph: A 42-year-old woman and her 8-year-old daughter were killed at the intersection of 210th Street and 64th Avenue, in the Oakland Gardens section of the borough.

headline.main: 2 Are Killed and 4 Injured in Car Crash in Queens
